title: Khalil Mack trade breakdown, what are the Raiders doing, cut day (Football 09/03)
description:
Will Brinson and Bryant McFadden are LIVE from Fort Lauderdale to break down the latest news around the NFL, including Khalil Mack being traded from the Raiders to the Bears, Martavis Bryant being cut by Oakland, AJ McCarron being traded from Buffalo to Oakland and all the other news and notes around the NFL.
